# Loan Detail with Proof

A React-based web app for managing loans with signature and video proof to prevent fraud.

## Features
- Borrower details entry
- Interest calculation (annual & monthly)
- Digital signature
- Video proof recording
- Timestamped records
- Payment chart

## Setup
1. Clone the repo.
2. Run `npm install`.
3. Run `npm start`.
4. Open http://localhost:3000.

## Deploy
Use Vercel or Netlify for free hosting.

## Note
This is a demo. Add backend (Node.js) and database for production. Ensure legal compliance.
